snippet.title: Bwirds Playdate Review.
snippet.description:
Quick review of Bwirds for Playdate by ThreeThreeThree Games.  Sweet word game combining anagram word-play, thematic challenges, fun graphics and pleasing music.  What not to like?

Catalogue $5: https://play.date/games/bwirds/
